<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ح ل س:</span> <span class="c2">(حِلْسُ)</span> الْبَيْتِ كِسَاءٌ يُبْسَطُ تَحْتَ حُرِّ الثِّيَابِ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«كُنْ حِلْسَ بَيْتِكَ»</span> أَيْ لَا تَبْرَحْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>